<p>Arts &amp; Humanities</p>
<h2>Zwischen Apokalypse und Wachstumsillusion: Warum wir neue Hoffnung brauchen</h2>
</header>
<footer><div class="post-meta"><span class="show-for-medium">Olivia Mitscherlich-Schönherr | </span>02.05.2024</div></footer>
</article>
</a>
</div>
<div class="teaser columns small-12 left-post-thumbnail widget small-12 left-post-thumbnail widget">
<a href="https://blog.degruyter.com/ai-literature-will-chatgpt-be-the-author-of-your-next-favourite-novel/" title="AI Literature: Will ChatGPT Be the Author of Your Next Favourite Novel?">
<div class="shadow"></div>
<div class="img" style="background-image:url('https://blog.degruyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/AI-reader-800x800.jpg')"></div>
<article>
<header>
<p>Arts &amp; Humanities</p>
